"Project" refers to the PLC-CORE-MDE system, including firmware, software, web server, simulator, hardware designs, documentation, schematics, PCB files, and related materials.

"Author" refers to Martín Entraigas, creator of PLC-CORE-MDE.

"Commercial use" means any use involving sale, manufacturing for sale, paid services, or integration into products sold to third parties.

"Compatible hardware" means external modules or devices designed to work with PLC-CORE-MDE without copying the full system.

